### 2. Push to GitHub (10 minutes)

```bash
# Initialize Git
git init
git add .
git commit -m "Initial commit - SchoolSync Pro"

# Create GitHub repo and push
git remote add origin https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/schoolsync-pro.git
git branch -M main
git push -u origin main
```

### 3. Deploy to Render (15 minutes)

1. Sign up at [render.com](https://render.com)
2. Connect GitHub repository
3. Create new Web Service
4. Configure:
   - Build: `pip install -r requirements.txt`
   - Start: `gunicorn --worker-class eventlet -w 1 app:app`
5. Set environment variables:
   ```
   SECRET_KEY = [generate with: python -c "import secrets; print(secrets.token_hex(32))"]
   DEBUG = False
   ```
6. Deploy!

